    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Male genital capsule of Cnemonis spp. 1, 2, C. kondratieffi sp. nov. 1, caudal view. 2, lateral view. 3, 4, C. lepida sp. nov. 3, caudal view. 4, lateral view." ;
