<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241212>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Dorsal view of Cnemomis spp. 9, C. gracilis (Dallas) (female). 10, C. kondratieffi sp. nov. (male). 11, C. lepida sp. nov. (female). 12, C. nigroscutellata sp. nov. (female)." ;
